Paper: hep-th/9311073

Date: 1993-11-11

Title: 2D Ising Model with a Defect Line

Authors: D.C.Cabra and C.M.Na\'on

Comments: 8 pages, report La Plata 93-08

Journal-ref: Mod. Phys. Lett. A9 (1994) 2107-2112

We study the two-dimensional Ising model with a defect line and evaluatemultipoint energy correlation functions using non-perturbativefield-theoretical methods. We also discuss the evaluation of the two spincorrelator on the defect line.